<p></div></div><br />
<strong>Compiling:</strong><br />
gcc client.c -o client<br />
gcc server.c -o server</p>
<p><strong>Output:</strong> </p>
<pre>
Client:Hello message sent
Hello from server
Server:Hello from client
Hello message sent</pre>
